sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Provider Mac
    participant S as install.sh
    participant API as Coordinator
    participant MDM as MicroMDM + SCEP
    participant A as Apple MDA

    S->>API: POST /v1/enroll {serial}
    API-->>S: .mobileconfig (SCEP + MDM + ACME)
    S->>P: Install profile
    P->>MDM: Enroll via SCEP identity
    MDM-->>P: MDM check-in complete
    API->>MDM: SecurityInfo + DeviceInformation(nonce)
    MDM->>P: Send commands
    P->>A: Request MDA cert chain
    A-->>P: Apple-signed certificate
    P->>P: Generate SE P-256 key
    P->>API: Register {attestation blob, X25519 pub}
    API->>API: Verify SE sig, check MDA chain,<br/>cross-check SecurityInfo
    API-->>P: Trust level: hardware
